INSTALLATION
------------

1. From your terminal window, execute the following command
	
	make

   It will compile the program into a single executable file named "email" in
   the same directory

2. To send a given RFC-822 formatted file as email, execute the following command

	email path/to/your_file

   Replacing path/to/your_file by the relative path to your RFC-822 formatted file.
   E.g.

	email test001.txt
	email test002.txt

3. To view more information about the program, execute the following command

	email help
